- ditch the App::Rad stuff in favor of a Moo object struct
- pick a less verbose API 

IDEAS:

alias t='/usr/bin/env timetrax.pl'

[RECORD TIME]
t PROJECT TASK   : start doing task on project

[REPORTS]
t                : overall report
t PROJECT        : project reprot
t report PROJECT : project report
t csv PROJECT    : project report in csv

[CONFIG]
t config                   : review entire config file
t config PROJECT           : review just this project's configs
t config PROJECT KEY       : review this aspect of a project config 
t config PROJECT KEY VALUE : set/update this key for this project
